              of technology to create meaningful impact. My journey combines full-stack development expertise 
              with a deep interest in NLP research, all guided by strong project management principles.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
              What sets me apart is my disciplined approach to execution and unwavering focus on delivering 
              tangible results. I don't just start projects; I complete them with excellence, always keeping 
              the end goal in sight.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Skills Grid */}
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            {/* Skill Items */}
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-200/50 
                         backdrop-blur-sm border border-accent/10 hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
                <span class="text-white/70">Problem Solver & Developer</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-primary/40"></span>
                Core Focus Areas
              </h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                {[
                  'Full Stack Development',
                  'NLP Research & Applications',
                  'Project Management',
                  'System Architecture'
                ].map(skill => (
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/60 group-hover:bg-primary 
                               transition-colors"></span>
                    <span class="text-white/70 group-hover:text-white/90 transition-colors">{skill}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-primary/40"></span>
                Tech Arsenal
              </h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {[
                  'React/Next.js', 'Node.js', 'Python',
                  'NLP', 'TypeScript', 'PostgreSQL',
                  'AWS', 'Docker', 'Git'
                ].map(tech => (
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary/90 
                             border border-primary/20 hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    {tech}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Vision */}
          <div class="space-y-4 p-6 rounded-xl bg-dark-200/50 border border-primary/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-primary/40"></span>
              Long-term Vision
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              To bridge the gap between innovative technology and practical business needs through disciplined 
              execution and result-oriented solutions, while continuously pushing the boundaries of what's possible 
              in full-stack development and NLP research.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* CTA */}
          <div class="pt-4 flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a
              href="#contact"
              class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#9b111e] to-[#ff1616] text-white rounded-lg
                     overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-[#9b111e]/20 hover:shadow-[#ff1616]/20
                     transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 active:translate-y-0"
            >
              <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2 font-medium">
                Let's Build Something Amazing
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" 
                     fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                        d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff1616] to-[#9b111e] opacity-0 
                          group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Right Column - Image */}
        <div class="relative max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-none order-first lg:order-last">
          <div class="relative aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/mypic.jpeg" 
              alt="Aayush518" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-105 hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-500"
              style="object-position: 50% 20%;"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark-100/80 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          
          {/* Decorative Elements */}
          <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-32 sm:w-40 h-32 sm:h-40 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-32 sm:w-40 h-32 sm:h-40 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>